Description: The Monaco Collection combines the class and elegance that has made the area famous with whimsical swirls that are inspired by neighboring France. Hand-forged, warm finishes, exclusive to Kalco, are combined with either the Black Iridescent shade or the Pearlescent Glass shade, also exclusive to Kalco, to create a series of lighting pieces that are entirely unique and stylish.

Title: Tall Wall Bracket
Description: The Keller Collection combines gentle slopes with looping, twisting iron to create a collection that is at once understated, modern and elegant. This unique combination of iron shapes is highlighted by Kalco`s exclusive finishes and simple, candle-like lights to create a functional art piece.

Title: One Light Wall Bracket
Description: The Tribecca Collection was inspired by the Art Nouveau style that dominated the TriBeCa area of NYC at the time of it`s initial conversion from industrial to residential. The array of curves that combine the industrial and the artistic are enhanced by Kalco`s exclusive warm finishes. The hand-crafted glass shades are delicately folded and seem to hang precariously from organically shaped stems to generate pieces that are all at once vintage and modern.

Title: Long Wall Sconce
Description: The Santa Barbara Collection was inspired by Colonial Mexico`s Mission Churches and Cathedrals. The long history of hand-crafted wrought iron, shared by both Mexico and Kalco, come together to create a series of lighting pieces that are made versatile by Kalco`s extensive selection of exclusive, hand-crafted shades.
